    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Discretization error, software quality assurance, relevance of QoIs, and numerical code verification all achieved levels at or above requirements. Output comparison and test conditions satisfy minimum requirements. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the intended use of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
